high_descs: walk over to the white kitchen table
grab a spoon off of the table
walk over to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter
place the spoon inside the cup under the coffee spout
grab the cup off of the coffee maker
bring the cup over to the black table left of the kitchen counter
place the cup on the black table
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a spoon in it on top of a black table

high_descs: Move to the white table.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Bring the spoon to the coffee machine.
Put the spoon in the mug on the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the small black table.
Put the mug on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the white table.
Pick up a spoon from the white table.
Turn around and go back to the coffee maker on your left counter after the sink.
Grab the mug from the coffee maker.
Put your spoon in the mug.
Turn left and go back to the white table.
Turn right to see a brown smaller table, put your mug on that table.
anns.task_desc: Getting a coffee mug with spoon.
